---
title: Speedy Chicken Breast Agrodolce with Buttery Mash and Roasted Veggies
description: Chicken, tossed in Italian sweet and sour sauce, served on buttery mash with roasted mushrooms and zucchini, is the perfect solution to what's for dinner!
